---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const title = "Professional English-Russian Translation Service	| Homepage";
const description =
    "EngRusTranslate provides English-Russian translation services to help you reach your global clients.";
---

<BaseLayout description={description} title={title}>
    <!-- <link slot="head" rel="preload" href="hero_image.svg" as="image" /> -->
    <main class="about-main">
        <img src="/sideview profile.jpg" class="about-img" alt="about us" />

        <section>
            <h1>About us</h1>
            <p>
                Hi there! I'm Pavel, the person behind [Your Firm's Name].
                Thanks for stopping by.
            </p>
            <p>
                I founded this company with a simple goal: to provide quality
                linguistic solutions to clients, who value <strong>
                    focused approach and narrow specialization</strong
                >.
            </p>
            <p>
                I and my trusted linguistic partners form a small team of <strong
                >
                    native Russian speakers</strong
                > passionate about bridging language gaps and <strong>
                    we only translate from English into our native language
                </strong> in order to offer the final product that is of the best
                quality.
            </p>
            <p>
                As linguists with <strong>
                    more than 15 years of professional experience</strong
                >
                working in-house for large multinational companies, I and my trusted
                linguistic partners understand the importance of focusing on what
                we do best.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h1>What we do</h1>
            <p>
                Our focus is clear: <strong>
                    expert translation, proofreading, revision and localization
                    services
                </strong> only in sectors we know inside out (Law/Contracts, Business/Finance,
                Investments/Securities Trading, Marketing, IT). Laser-focused specialization
                in only one language pair: <strong> English - Russian</strong>.
                Our focus on the specific language pair allows for unparalleled
                precision and cultural accuracy.
            </p>
            <p>
                Whether you're dealing with contracts, looking to expand your
                market reach with a compelling pitch, or needing your website to
                speak in a new tongue, we're here to help. We will help your
                brand speak like a local across all channels, consistently, and
                in the most culturally-relevant way.
            </p>
            <p>
                We also offer post-editing of machine translation output,
                bilingual review of third-party translations as an external
                quality assurance partner.
            </p>
            <p>
                Our clients include translation agencies and leading language
                service providers from all over the world.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h1>What makes us different</h1>
            <p>
                <strong> Specialized Expertise:</strong> We're not generalists. Our
                work in the English - Russian language pair means you get translations
                that are not just accurate but culturally attuned.
            </p>
            <p>
                <strong> Consistent Quality:</strong> Every project, big or small,
                gets our personal attention. We bring 15 years of experience to the
                table promising you the same high standards every time.
            </p>
            <p>
                <strong> Professional Integrity:</strong> We're all about transparency
                and trust.
            </p>
            <p>
                <strong> Quality Assurance:</strong> Our rigorous quality check ensures
                every translation hits the mark on accuracy, fluency, and industry
                relevance.
            </p>
            <p>
                <strong> Confidentiality and Security:</strong> Your documents are
                in safe hands, treated with the highest levels of privacy and care.
            </p>
            <p>
                <strong> Reasonable prices:</strong> Being a small operation with
                little overhead costs and no intermediaries in the process, we can
                afford to provide quality services at reasonable prices.
            </p>
            <p>
                We arenâ€™t a traditional language business, we are genuine and
                our communication is always honest: we will always offer the
                best solution, the most cost-effective, and the one we believe
                to be fair to you and care about your success as much as you do.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h1>A bit more info</h1>
            <p>
                [Your Firm's Name] is not just a business, but as <strong>
                    a commitment to quality, efficiency, and service.</strong
                > If you're looking for a partner who genuinely cares about getting
                your message across as much as you do, do not hesitate to reach out.
                We are happy to hear from you!
            </p>
        </section>
    </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
    .about-main {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 1em;
        margin: 0.5em;
        padding: 0.5em;
    }

    .about-img {
        width: 100%;
        object-fit: contain;
    }

    section {
        padding: 1em;
        border-width: 0.1em;
        border-style: solid;
        border-image: linear-gradient(to top, #f4fb3a, #f23636) 1;
        text-align: justify;
    }
    p {
        padding: 0.5em;
    }
</style>
